### TaksiWebApi Drivers Testing
@baseUrl = https://localhost:7050

### Get all drivers
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/drivers

###

### Get driver by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/drivers/1

###

### Get driver by phone number
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/drivers/phone/+1234567890

###

### Get driver by email
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/drivers/email/driver@example.com

###

### Get active drivers
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/drivers/active

###

### Get drivers paginated
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/drivers/paginated?pageNumber=1&pageSize=5

###

### Get total drivers count
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/drivers/count

###

### Get active drivers count
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/drivers/active/count

###

### Search drivers by name
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/drivers/search?searchTerm=John

###

### Get drivers by date range
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/drivers/date-range?startDate=2024-01-01&endDate=2024-12-31

###

### Get drivers by vehicle plate
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/drivers/vehicle-plate/ABC123

###
